===Pronunciation===
* UK {{IPA|[əˈpɒkəlɪps]}}
* US {{IPA|[əˈpɑkəlɪps]}}
* {{SAMPA|/@"pQk@lIps/}}

===Hyphenation===
:a&middot;poc&middot;a&middot;lypse

===Noun===
{{en-noun-unc}}

# {{uncountable}} (''Religion'') The written account of a revelation of hidden things given by God to a chosen prophet.
# {{uncountable}} The end of life on earth or all.
# {{rfv-sense}} {{countable}} A day of severe destruction or death.
# {{rfv-sense}} {{countable}} A confrontation that will change the course of history.

